% =============================================================================
% references.bib -- BibLaTeX database
%
% This revision aligns with the Nova SBE Library's recommended style
% (Chicago Author-Date) and is meant to be compiled with the
% biblatex-chicago package using `authordate' as configured in main.tex.
%
% Key changes vs. the previous version:
%   - arXiv preprints are typed as @online with `eprint' / `eprinttype'
%     and `url' fields, so biblatex-chicago renders them properly
%     ("Author. Year. \"Title.\" arXiv:XXXX.XXXXX.") rather than as if
%     the journal were literally called "arXiv preprint arXiv:...".
%   - DOIs and URLs added where available.
%   - Reid Gemini entry now lists the first 7 authors + others, so
%     Chicago Author-Date can produce "first 7 + et al." correctly.
%   - Llama 3 technical report points to the actual arXiv ID.
%   - Olsson induction-heads entry now carries the Transformer Circuits URL.
%
% NOTE: biblatex-chicago with maxbibnames=7 / minbibnames=7 (set in main.tex)
% will automatically truncate entries with >10 authors to "first 7 + et al."
% in the reference list. The full author list is still kept in this file so
% future format changes do not lose data.
% =============================================================================


